25 Jun 2015
-----------

0. How to use this common utility in a project
   In that project's Build Path -> Configure Build Path... -> Projects Tab -> Add
   
1. Finally decided to create a utility package. Common ones are:
   . network
   . data parsing
   
   commonly used external libraries are:
